data.description: Welcome home to main-level living in the desirable Stoneway community. This adorable rambler boasts tons of natural light, a large primary suite has a 5-piece bath and walk-in closet and has 3 additional bedrooms, an open-concept kitchen and family room that features a cozy fireplace, plus a comfortable, separate living room. You could even turn the fourth bedroom into a home office! Keep the temp just right with the furnace and A/C. Your large corner lot is spacious, and the fully fenced backyard offers lots of opportunities while being low maintenance but with room to create your own garden. The primary bedroom is currently being used as a classroom. Photos are virtually staged as an example of what is possible.
